{"tid":453712,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[女主播]梁凱寧討論區3","createTime":"2017-10-31T12:19:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-31T13:30:29.000Z","uid":61384,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5eb88e2e8665cc4d2440a173593e51e536b63fb9","tid":453712,"uid":61384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">34E人氣大台女主播梁凱寧討論區</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">女主播梁凱寧連登相關討論區，多多指教<br />\n開始原因 : 因為都見到有好多粉絲但係連登未有討論區，所以想開個區分享及擺放cap圖</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/22886305_10213539059766776_5764147387794797476_n.jpg?oh=7b0e0e36af08ede9da432fbdb0e75af0&amp;oe=5A7337CB\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F22886305_10213539059766776_5764147387794797476_n.jpg%3Foh%3D7b0e0e36af08ede9da432fbdb0e75af0%26oe%3D5A7337CB&h=efc1fb49&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/23130505_10213539068807002_5173738986933537056_n.jpg?oh=cfba86d9c0a6468e288faa8935a5df33&amp;oe=5A6E37AA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F23130505_10213539068807002_5173738986933537056_n.jpg%3Foh%3Dcfba86d9c0a6468e288faa8935a5df33%26oe%3D5A6E37AA&h=671e941e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n旨在分享梁凱寧相關資訊，歡迎分享Cap圖包括<br />\n1 當天新聞造型<br />\n2 擔任主持的新聞資訊節目<br />\n3 日常生活照update<br />\n備註：嚴禁分享其他女主播cap圖，避免混亂及離題 <br />\n<br />\n官方資訊：<br />\n梁凱寧IG : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/maggie_tvbnews/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fmaggie_tvbnews%2F&d=aDAjh%2BXfj1h18Xwx2p8ORviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=e75aa3f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/maggie_tvbnews/</a><br />\n梁凱寧微博 : 未有，但有粉絲開設帳戶定時擺放cap圖<a href=\"http://www.weibo.com/u/2327703620?refer_flag=1001030001_&amp;nick=%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%83%88%E7%83%88&amp;is_all=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.weibo.com%2Fu%2F2327703620%3Frefer_flag%3D1001030001_%26nick%3D%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2583%2588%25E7%2583%2588%26is_all%3D1&d=aDAjh%2BXfj1h18Xwx2p8ORviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=9ab5093d\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.weibo.com/u/2327703620?refer_flag=1001030001_&amp;nick=%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E7%83%88%E7%83%88&amp;is_all=1</a><br />\n(如有官方微博將後補Link)</blockquote>"},{"pid":"41e3fe5eb58e3217ac2d55e649824deb86097752","tid":453712,"uid":61384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T12:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dcvmj9of\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdcvmj9of&h=eff05a87&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://holland.pk/7d29e6pw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7d29e6pw&h=b369a779&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://holland.pk/0xs4zboj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0xs4zboj&h=b366f8de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u4kg9v5s\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu4kg9v5s&h=ee585e07&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://holland.pk/cp9odjka\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fcp9odjka&h=fb2e2139&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://holland.pk/31gyj2pk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F31gyj2pk&h=3ac385fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/mefirnjl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fmefirnjl&h=53cedd3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無綫730 一小時新聞 (2017-10-31)"},{"pid":"9fe64f76cf5e09b4f59c6ab84a0718061d841f3f","tid":453712,"uid":61384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-31T13:28:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"htt